Package: survey160r
Title: R Client for Survey160 Data
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lennon", "Shimokawa", email = "lshimokawa@survey160.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
    )
Description: Access Survey160 campaign data from R. Supports reading
    campaign results from Google Cloud Storage and triggering fresh exports
    via the Survey160 API using service account authentication.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
