    googleCloudStorageR (>= 0.7.0),
    httr,
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    mockery,
    withr,
    lintr,
    covr
Config/testthat/edition: 3
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
